name: Grauen no Torikago: Kapitel 6: Senritsu
overview: Grauen no Torikago Kapitel 6: Senritsu (グラウエンの鳥籠 Kapitel 6 「戦慄」) is the last chapter of Grauen no Torikago movie. It contains about 60 episodes of one minute each. Not only is Senritsu the rarest of the six discs in the series, it is often cited as one of the rarest Dreamcast discs in existence.
